Description: Provides functions to estimate Inequality of Opportunity (IOP)
    and the Gini index for complex survey designs. Supports stratified and
    clustered sampling with analytical (influence function) variance
    estimation, an ablation study that quantifies each circumstance's
    contribution to relative IOP, and a cluster-bootstrap test comparing
    ablation contributions between two data sets.
